This project is a modified distribution of mailgun-ses-proxy.

Upstream project:
https://github.com/typetale-app/mailgun-ses-proxy

The upstream project is licensed under the GNU Affero General Public
License v3.0. This repository keeps the same AGPL-3.0 license.

Notable changes in this distribution include:
- Ghost newsletter compatibility improvements.
- Amazon SES event mapping to Mailgun-compatible events.
- Mailgun suppression endpoint compatibility for Ghost.
- Docker, GHCR, and deployment documentation.
- Security and packaging cleanup for reusable deployments.
